reviewText: Just Love this DVD.  If you want a good DVD of Al Green.  This is it.  He puts on an amazing show.  LOVE  IT!!!

I love Al Green, but didn't find this to be one of his
greatest. Not enough singing for me. :0(

I got fooled again.
This is Al Green in Anaheim
'Everything's Gonna Be Alright'
Just repackaged.
Got me again!
